message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you this excellent product.  I'm asking $150 for it. It's a great deal!
Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. However, $150 is much higher than what I'm willing to pay. I can find similar products for much less. I'd be willing to pay $60 for it.
Bob, I understand you're looking for a good deal.  While $60 is too low for me, I'm willing to come down to $130.  This product is truly worth it.
